channel.title: Some of my work from a while ago that I never showed off
channel.description:
The title says it all basically. Hah. Most of these will probably, in your opinion...stink. Keep in mind, most of these were [size=24pt]A WHILE AGO[/size] here they are though. If someone wants something I will make the mqo stickied to this topic...you can put it in your client from there...Just credit me.
[size=18pt]Gore Reaper (Or a new dragon scim O_O)[/size] [URL=http://img214.imageshack.us/i/gorereaper.png/][IMG]http://img214.imageshack.us/img214/286/gorereaper.png[/img][/URL] 572 vertices 1120 tri's
[size=18pt]"Dragon Claws" - a gag model [/size] :P [URL=http://img684.imageshack.us/i/dragonclaw.png/][IMG]http://img684.imageshack.us/img684/6217/dragonclaw.png[/img][/URL] Who cares about this model's poly count...its a gag.
[size=18pt] No-Name Sword - old model, real old. [/size] [URL=http://img139.imageshack.us/i/swordnoname.png/][IMG]http://img139.imageshack.us/img139/8043/swordnoname.png[/img][/URL] Low poly count.
[size=18pt] No-Name Axe - old model, more new than previous though. [/size] [URL=http://img39.imageshack.us/i/nonameaxe.png/][IMG]http://img39.imageshack.us/img39/6540/nonameaxe.png[/img][/URL] 424 vertics 696 tri's ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ There you go...some of my old models.
